5. RACI Framework
Meaning of RACI
R – Responsible (does the work)
A – Accountable (owns the outcome)
C – Consulted (provides input)
I – Informed (kept updated)
Purpose:
Clarifies ownership.
Prevents confusion.
Improves communication.
Keeps projects organized.

