## 8. My Reflection
One of my biggest takeaways from this module is that Product Management is far more than building products. A Product Manager connects customers, business goals, engineering, design, marketing, sales, and other stakeholders to deliver products that solve real problems. Success depends on continuous communication, strategic thinking, collaboration, and making informed decisions throughout the product's entire lifecycle.

